OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNew rules ban many         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsingle-use plastics in     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FScotland                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, New rules have come into force banning 
OL,6, businesses in Scotland from providing  
OL,7, single use plastic items such as       
OL,8, cutlery, plates and stirrers.          
OL,10,FPolystyrene food containers and cups   
OL,11,Fare also covered by the new ban as well
OL,12,Fas plastic straws and balloon sticks.  
OL,14,FThe Scottish government said it was the
OL,15,Ffirst part of the UK to ban many       
OL,16,F"problematic" single-use plastics.     
OL,18,FIt estimated about 700 million of these
OL,19,Fsingle-use items are currently used in 
OL,20,FScotland every year.                   
